<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">McCathern becomes emotional while talking with a friend about the lasting health impacts of the Flint water crisis. “That’s the only reason I’m here [in Flint], is because so much injustice to humans, to humanity.”</span>
    
    
    
