<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="36.0">Medlin said she uses her food stamp benefits on bottled water deliveries from Walmart for Audrina’s bottles. For her first months, Medlin relied on the infant’s father to bathe her at his home outside the city.</p>
        
    
                    

